title: How do I uninstall pre-installed applications?
answer:
On the home screen, touch and hold the application you want to uninstall, drag it to the trash can icon, and follow the onscreen instructions to uninstall it.

![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141204204248325001.jpg)

System applications cannot be uninstalled.

![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141204204249808002.png)

The figures are for your reference only. The actual screens may vary.
